{
  "texts": [
    "Various attack methods against VAE and VAE-GAN models were developed [30]- [32], including classifier-based attacks, attacks using the VAE loss function, and latent space attacks.",
    "These methods aimed to generate adversarial examples that would be reconstructed as images from different classes.",
    "Recent research has expanded to investigating attacks on the encoder output of hierarchical VAEs, considering the higher-level latent variables [9].",
    "Most existing research on VAE attacks has focused on manipulating the input or latent space to affect reconstruction output.",
    "Our approach, however, differs significantly from these previous works."
  ]
}